# LSSD
The repository save the code of LSSD (AFTER submitted to IJCAI2022).

## Command line args
`--pure-batch` If used, each batch contain samples from only one language pair.

`--LS-epoch`  # If used, valid losses will be recorded for each language pair.

`--LSSD-MNMT`  # If used, apply LSSD on the MNMT (--task translation_multi_single_epoch)
